*Shvatiš* da je život težak (You understand that life is hard).

*Shvatiti* ćeš da je odgovornost bitna (You will understand that responsibility is important).

*Shvaćamo* da je promena neizbežna (We understand that change is inevitable).

*Shvatite* da se ništa ne može postići bez rada (Understand that nothing can be achieved without work).

*Shvatajući* to, postali smo svesni sopstvenih mogućnosti (By understanding it, we became aware of our own possibilities).